      *､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､*
      *  PROGRAM ID.   :  ALBRCC                                       *
      *  PROGRAM       :  kｩｮhmﾞﾆﾞｮn CALCULATIO (yﾆﾞｬ[ﾇ43)
      *                                                                *
      *  UPDATE DAY   :                                                *
      *                                                                *
      *､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､*
      *  EXPLANATION
      *  WHEN I WANT TO EXAMINE kｩｮhmﾞﾆﾞｮn OF CODE 39
      *         PMAREA = 'CODE39'
      *         PMBYTE = '006'
      *  INPUT
      *         PMCHK  = 'W'
      *         PMRTCD = ' '
      *  TURN IT OVER
      *､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､*
      *  ATTENTION
      *  kｩｮhmﾞﾆﾞｮn ENTERS PMCHK, AND PMAREA DOESN'T CHANGE
      *  AND I TURN OVER PMRTCD='1' WHEN THERE IS THE CHARACTER
      *  WHICH IS CONVERSION IMPOSSIBILITY IN PMAREA
      *       (IT IS PMRTCD=' ' IN NORMAL EXIT)
      *､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､､*
     H            Y/                                    1
     E*****************************************************************
     E                    CHR    43  43  1
     E                    DEC    40  43  2 0
     E*
     E                    ARA       100  1               mﾞｰj
     I*****************************************************************
     I*ﾎｧｰﾓnﾞﾈｮn
     I            DS
     I                                        1 100 W@AREA
     I                                        1 100 ARA
     C***************************************************************
     C*mﾞｰjﾞ､ﾒﾇn
     C***************************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PMAREA100        *ﾎｧｰﾓnﾞ
     C                     PARM           PMBYTE  3        * ﾏcﾃcijﾇc
     C                     PARM           PMCHK   1        * kｩｮhmﾞﾆﾞｮn
     C                     PARM           PMRTCD  1        * ﾒjｰ]ﾃｰnﾞ
     C***************************************************************
     C*MAIN
     C***************************************************************
     C                     EXSR #INIT
     C*
     C                     EXSR #CHECK
     C*END
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C***************************************************************
     C*
     C***************************************************************
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
     C*
     C                     MOVELPMAREA    W@AREA           *ﾎｧｰﾓnﾞ
     C                     MOVELPMBYTE    W@CNT   30       * ﾏcﾃcijﾇc
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    PMRTCD           * ﾒjｰ]ﾃｰnﾞ
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
     C*****************************************************************
     C* kｩｮhmﾞﾆﾞｮnibﾅ](yﾆﾞｬ[ﾇ43)
     C*****************************************************************
     C           #CHECK    BEGSR
     C                     MOVEL*ZERO     W@WA    50
     C* yﾆﾞ ﾇcﾆﾞmﾞｰj
     C           1         DO   W@CNT     I       30
     C                     Z-ADD1         J       20
     C           ARA,I     LOKUPCHR,J                    50
     C           *IN50     IFEQ '1'
     C                     ADD  DEC,J     W@WA
     C                     ELSE
     C* vaj[obmﾞｰj
     C                     MOVEL'1'       PMRTCD           * ﾒjｰ]ﾃｰnﾞ
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C*
     C           PMRTCD    IFNE '1'
     C* ﾃﾞcib･43mﾞﾝﾓ
     C           W@WA      DIV  43        W@SYOU  50       *
     C                     MVR            W@AMAL  20
     C* auﾒ･ﾇcﾆﾞmﾞｰj yﾆﾞ
     C           1         DO   43        K       20
     C           W@AMAL    IFEQ DEC,K
     C                     MOVE CHR,K     PMCHK
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C                     ENDSR
